          <div style="font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--charcoal);margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Improving Quality &amp; Outcomes</div>
          <p style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--warm-brown);line-height:1.6;margin:0;">A 2012 analysis of nearly 80 research trials found patients with depression and anxiety had significantly better outcomes under a collaborative care model than standard primary care — with benefits in medication use, quality of life, and patient satisfaction.</p>
