          <div style="font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--charcoal);margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Reducing Utilization of Acute Services</div>
          <p style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--warm-brown);line-height:1.6;margin:0;">Robert Young Center implemented PCMHs integrating BH into primary care — reducing ED visits by 46%, psychiatric admissions by 50%, and medical admissions for BH-diagnosed patients by nearly 17%.</p>
