          <h4>Use Data for Insights &amp; Action</h4>
          <p>Intentionally design a data collection and analytics program to understand BH impact, identify at-risk individuals, and articulate the value of BH care. Explore behavioral biomarkers and leverage new data liquidity requirements to build real clinical predictive modeling.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="opp-card">
          <div style="font-size:0.6rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--warm-peach);margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Opportunity 3</div>
          <h4>Use Holistic Outcome Assessments</h4>
          <p>Replace subjective GAF scores with multi-faceted outcome frameworks (WHODAS 2.0, HoNOS) that account for complex cases and measure progress toward shared clinician and patient goals. You can't reimburse based on outcomes without fairly measuring them first.</p>
        </div>

